SELECT
  ID, ax, ay, az, gx, gy, gz, mx, my, mz, heading, pitch, roll
FROM IMU_data
ORDER BY ID ASC

SELECT
  ID,
  counts,
  counts * 0.0859655832 AS mm,
  AVG(counts) OVER (
      ORDER BY ID
      ROWS BETWEEN 19 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW
  ) AS mean_last_20,
  AVG(counts) OVER (
      ORDER BY ID
      ROWS BETWEEN 19 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW
  ) * 0.0859655832 AS mean_mm
FROM Digital_data
WHERE ID BETWEEN 0 AND 11884
ORDER BY ID ASC;
